HEADWORD: Neapolitan ice cream
<hw>Neapolitan ice cream</hw>
}</mhw>. <sd>(a)</sd> <def>An ice or ice cream containing eggs as well
as cream.</def> <sd>(b)</sd> <def>An ice or ice cream prepared in
layers, as vanilla, strawberry, and chocolate ice cream, and orange or
lemon water ice.</def>⟦br⟧
